on.", "bbox": [85.5, 1224.1, 150.9, 1247.2]}, {"text": "Depreciation expense on property and equipment was $2.5 billion, $1.7 billion, and $1.0 billion, which includes", "bbox": [135.5, 1267.9, 1074.4, 1290.9]}, {"text": "amortization of property and equipment acquired under capital lease obligations of $826 million, $510 million, and $335", "bbox": [85.5, 1292.9, 1097.8, 1315.9]}, {"text": "million for 2013, 2012, and 2011. Gross assets remaining under capital leases were $4.2 billion and $2.3 billion as of", "bbox": [85.5, 1317.9, 1065.8, 1341.0]}, {"text": "December 31, 2013 and 2012. Accumulated depreciation associated with capital leases was $1.9 billion and $1.1 billion as of", "bbox": [85.5, 1342.9, 1134.8, 1366.0]}, {"text": "December 31, 2013 and 2012. Cash paid for interest on capital leases was $41 million, $51 million, and $44 million for 2013,", "bbox": [85.5, 1367.9, 1138.4, 1391.0]}, {"text": "2012, and 2011.", "bbox": [85.5, 1392.9, 219.0, 1416.0]}, {"text": "We capitalize construction in progress and record a corresponding long-term liability for build-to-suit lease agreements", "bbox": [132.3, 1436.7, 1130.3, 1459.7]}, {"text": "where we are considered the owner, for accounting purposes, during the construction period. For buildings under build-to-suit", "bbox": [85.5, 1461.7, 1140.4, 1484.8]}, {"text": "lease arrangements where we have taken occupancy, which do not qualify for sales recognition under the sale-leaseback", "bbox": [85.5, 1486.7, 1091.1, 1509.8]}, {"text": "accounting guidance, we determined that we continue to be the deemed owner of these buildings. This is principally due to our", "bbox": [85.5, 1511.7, 1148.3, 1534.8]}]}